title.en: Watashi wo Dekiaishi Sugiru Danna-sama wa Konya mo Furete Kuremasen
Otoko Un ga E Rank na no de Sekai no Yami Ochi Kamisama ni Metoraremashita
Furin Aite ga Mama Haha Datta no de Rien wo Keikaku Itashimasu
Hametsu End Kara Gyakkou Shitara, Nishuume wa Nazeka Aisare Route deshita - Yami Ochi Reijou wa Ouji e no Fukushuu wo Akiramenai (no ni Dekiaisareru)
Itsuwari no Inaka Reijou, Osananajimi no Ouji-sama wo Kouryaku-chuu
Kouri no Koushaku-sama to Karisome no Hanayome - Kozukuri Shitara Rikon no Hazu ga, Naze ka Chouaisaretemasu
Waru Nadakaki Reikoku Ouji wa Watashi no Koto Shika Aisenai
Ouhi ni Naru Yotei Deshita ga, Nise Seijo no Omei wo Kiserareta no de Toubou Shitara, Koutaishi ni Dekiai Saremashita. Sochira mo Douzo Oshiawase ni
Kusuriya Keiei shite Mitara, Rieki ga Osoroshii Koto ni narimashita - Heimin Dakara to Tsuihousareta Moto Kyuutei Renkinjutsushi no Monogatari
Moto Dorei no Migawari Hime wa, Reiketsu Ouji no Hanayome ni Natte Dekiaisareru
"Akage no Yakutatazu" to Kubi ni natta Maryokunashi no Majo desu ga, "Yakusou no Chishiki ga Hanpanai!" to Ouritsu Kenkyuujo ni Soku Saiyou Saremashita.
Umagoya Kurashi no Goreijou wa Angai Ryoushu ni Muiteiru?
